# Preview

This repository's previewable surface is the static documentation site in
`website/`. There is no package-manager dev server, login, or seed data.

Start the preview server from the repository root:

```sh
python3 -m http.server 4173 --directory website
```

Expected URL:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:4173/
```

Verify readiness with:

```sh
curl -fsS http://127.0.0.1:4173/ >/dev/null
```
